Cyber Claw:








After staring down at the other raptor, Cyber Claw was pulled from the 
ground, held by powerful jaws. Her mind instantly warned her: Megatron!

She instantly bit down on the creature's jaw, bitting deep and hard. There 
was no way she was going to give up yet. No, not after all this time of 
running and hidding. She wasn't going to die now.
